title: Huge Main Floor Unit for 10/1, Updated Kitchen/Bath, 2 Garage Spaces
posting_body: ['Huge Main Floor Unit Available October 1, High Ceilings, Updated Kitchen & Bath, 2 Garage Spaces Included', 'Property Address', '529 Portland Ave - #1 | St. Paul, MN 55102', 'Available: 10/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'Guardian Property Management |', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'With occupied units, we can only do a showing after an application is approved.', ' To apply, go to <URL>  Each adult would apply and upload last two pay statements and proof of other income.', 'Main floor unit available October 1 in Cathedral Hill neighborhood.', 'Hardwood floors and high ceilings throughout.', ' This apartment has a spacious living room as well as a full dining room.', ' The kitchen has been fully updated and is just off the dining room.', ' Both bedrooms are in the back of the apartment with a large updated bathroom just off the bedrooms.', " There's a long hallway from the front of the apartment to the back with storage closets.", 'This apartment includes two garage parking spaces.', "There's a fully fenced in back yard with patio, and there's laundry in the basement.", 'Highly sought after St. Paul location just one block off Summit Avenue.', '$50 application fee per adult', 'We check income (gross household income must be at least 3 times rent), credit (must be 600+), criminal and rental history', 'Rent includes water/sewer, trash & gas (heat)', 'Cats are okay with a $35/month pet fee per.', 'Sorry no dogs.', 'Call Dakota at', 'show contact info', 'for more information', 'Agent: Dakota DeHaven', 'BROKER: GUARDIAN PROPERTY MANAGEMENT AND SERVICES LLC', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 2BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 1,100', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,699.00', 'Available: 10/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $50.00', 'Security Deposit: $1,699.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
